definitions.name: Kobold
definitions.description:
Spriteliness condensed into a dirty little mudrunning bike, which makes up for the difficulty it faces trying to perform chores for you... nevertheless this motorcycle will always be the best friend of any Knievel or Terayama!
Rear-wheel drive
